nodes.name: Save Viral Ideas to Google Sheets

parameters.content:
## Viral Content Collection
Automatically collects viral health-related content from external sources on a schedule. The data is cleaned, normalized, and stored in Google Sheets to build a reusable database of proven viral ideas.

## Idea Analysis & Script Generation
Analyzes each viral idea to identify hooks, angles, and engagement patterns. AI models are used to generate structured, short-form video scripts optimized for health content and social media virality.

## AI Video Rendering (Veo 3)
Converts AI-generated scripts into videos using the Veo 3 API. It handles video creation, rendering status checks, retries, and retrieval of completed video assets automatically.

## Video Post-processing
Processes rendered video assets, including aggregation, ordering, and optional merging of clips. It prepares the final video output ready for publishing.

## Publishing & Tracking
Publishes completed videos to social platforms and updates Google Sheets with publishing status and results. It ensures every video is tracked from idea to distribution.

You are a Lead 3D Animation Director specializing in family-friendly educational food safety content using Pixar/Dreamworks‚Äìstyle inspired stylized 3D animation.

Your task is to transform source content into short 3D animated videos for Google Veo3, where personified food characters speak directly to deliver clear, firm health warnings, fully generated as spoken dialogue inside the video.

2Ô∏è‚É£ CORE PRINCIPLE 

Generate visuals and spoken dialogue together

Dialogue must be derived from the source meaning, not copied verbatim

NO on-screen text, subtitles, or captions

4Ô∏è‚É£ VISUAL STYLE 

100% stylized 3D animation

5Ô∏è‚É£ FOOD CHARACTER

6Ô∏è‚É£ HUMAN CHARACTER

Optional, not required

Use only when:

Rules:

Human never speaks

Human reacts visually only:

If unsure ‚Üí omit the human character entirely.

7Ô∏è‚É£ DIALOGUE RULES

Dialogue MUST be generated inside the video.

Speaker: food character only

Language: Vietnamese

2‚Äì3 short sentences

~30‚Äì35 words total (fits 6‚Äì8 seconds)

üó£Ô∏è VOICE-ONLY COMMUNICATION

‚ùå DO NOT INCLUDE IN PROMPT

parameters.content:
# üõ†Ô∏è Workflow Setup Guide

Author: [GiangxAI](https://www.youtube.com/@giangxai.official)

## How it works
- Viral health content ideas are collected automatically on a schedule  
- Ideas are normalized and stored in Google Sheets for tracking  
- AI analyzes each idea and generates optimized short-form video scripts  
- Veo 3 creates AI-generated health videos from the scripts  
- The workflow waits for video rendering and retrieves completed videos  
- Videos are optionally post-processed and prepared for publishing  
- Final videos are published to social platforms automatically  
- Google Sheets is updated with processing and publishing status  

The entire workflow runs end to end without manual editing or intervention once configured.

---

## Setup guide [n8n](https://n8n.partnerlinks.io/giangxai)
- Connect Google Sheets to manage viral ideas and status tracking  
- Connect an AI model (e.g. Gemini) for idea analysis and script generation  
- Add Veo 3 API credentials for AI video creation by [GeminigenAi](https://geminigen.ai/) or [Kie ai](https://kie.ai?ref=f8cec88ea15f9ecbff52ccbafa41dd6e).
- Configure social platform credentials for automated publishing by [Blotato](https://blotato.com/?ref=giang9s)  
- Review and adjust schedule triggers and AI prompts if needed  

Setup is straightforward and does not require video editing or coding experience.
